Based on this evaluation, management concluded that the Company&#8217;s internal control over financial reporting was effective as of December 31, 2022. The effectiveness of the Company&#8217;s internal control over financial reporting as of December 31, 2022 has been audited by PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP, an independent registered public accounting firm, as stated in its report which is included herein.

